title: Rex Stout Nero Wolfe Complete 47 Novel Audio Series the MDR
description:
From my extensive Audio Book collection, painstakingly edited from CD & Cassette in dawn of the digital audio age, I offer here Rex Stout's Nero Wolfe Series. It is the crown jewel of my collection and my all-time favorite series.

The series features:
-47 Novels 
-All in MP3 64Mbps CBR
-Separated into chapters & properly tagged
-All 47 were brilliantly narrated by Michael Prichard
